   Important notice for PMI-certified Project Management Professionals
   (PMPs):

   Attendance at the October 24th Executive Leadership Forum is equivalent
   to four (4) Professional Development Units (PDUs) toward maintaining a
   Project Management Professional (PMP) certification by the Project
   Management Institute (PMI). The reporting code for the ELF event is
   1038-ELFO24. For more information on PDUs, you can visit the PMI
   website at:
   http://www.pmi.org/certification/pdp/overview.htm#Activities
